    {
        "url": "/quotes/thomas_kail_762922",
        "quote": "As a kid, I wanted to be a sportscaster. On the radio. I loved the idea of painting a picture. I didn't want to be on TV. I wanted to be Jon Miller, who called all the Orioles games.",
